{"TopicId":199885,"ForumId":70,"TopicTitle":"Ghost image during scene change - Solved","CreatedByName":"SpacedInvader","CreatedById":106018,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-01-28T01:09:24Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"SpacedInvader","CreatedById":106018,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-01-28T01:09:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFor the last two days I\u0027ve been getting odd behavior during scene changes (i.e. from main menu to \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E, KCS to \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E, etc) where instead of going to a black screen for loading, I get a weird ghosted image of the previous scene like this:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022ecoO37T.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002289.75\u0022 height=\u0022674\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/ecoO37T.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022ar0bkek.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002289.75\u0022 height=\u0022673\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/ar0bkek.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAt first I thought it had to do with an nVidia driver that I\u0027d just updated, but I\u0027ve since rolled back and am still getting the same behavior. I don\u0027t think its something critical, but I\u0027d like to fix it anyway so I\u0027m wondering if anyone has ever seen anything like this in the past and if so, what can I do to fix it? Also, is it possible that this could be the result of a mod as I run quite a large modlist and more than a few were updated yesterday.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEDIT: I\u0027ve now tried removing all of the mods that were added / updated since the issue appeared and its still occurring so I don\u0027t believe its a mod related issue.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEDIT2: Solved with a complete uninstall, cleaning, and reinstall of older drivers. The Game Ready driver v461.40 was apparently the culprit and a rollback to v460.89 corrected the issue.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-01-28T07:31:56Z\u0022 title=\u002201/28/2021 07:31  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EJanuary 28, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by SpacedInvader\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"VoidCosmos","CreatedById":192336,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-01-28T08:01:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u0026lt;snip\u0026gt;\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-01-28T08:05:08Z\u0022 title=\u002201/28/2021 08:05  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EJanuary 28, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by VoidCosmos\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EWrong thread\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kielm","CreatedById":82247,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-01-29T12:11:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/106018-spacedinvader/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022106018\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/106018-spacedinvader/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@SpacedInvader\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0This is caused by NVIDIA MSAA setting, which is enabled when you choose the optimised options in Geforce Experience.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDon\u0027t use MSAA or revert that setting in NVIDIA control panel to avoid that ghosted image.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SpacedInvader","CreatedById":106018,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-01-29T22:50:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223916649\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022199885\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221611922280\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002282247\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Kielm\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 hours ago, Kielm said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/106018-spacedinvader/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022106018\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/106018-spacedinvader/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@SpacedInvader\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0This is caused by NVIDIA MSAA setting, which is enabled when you choose the optimised options in Geforce Experience.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDon\u0027t use MSAA or revert that setting in NVIDIA control panel to avoid that ghosted image.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks for clearing that up, at least now I know that it wasn\u0027t the new driver per-se, but rather a setting that it decided to impose on its own during install.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-01-29T22:51:05Z\u0022 title=\u002201/29/2021 10:51  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EJanuary 29, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by SpacedInvader\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}